text: Switch Tape is the debut extended play written and conducted by Australian singer, rapper and songwriter Tkay Maidza. The EP was originally released in October 2014 through Dew Process Records, containing debut single, entitled "U-Huh", but was then re-issued on 8 December 2015, containing newly released singles, entitled "M.O.B" and "Ghost". ==Track listing== ==References== Category:2014 EPs Category:Tkay Maidza albums
title: Switch Tape
